'''Ross Drummond''' (born 20 March 1994) is a Scottish [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Scottish Junior Football Association|Scottish Junior]] side [[Dundonald Bluebell F.C.|Dundonald Bluebell]].

==Career==
Drummond began his career with [[Burntisland Shipyard Amateur F.C.|Burntisland Shipyard Amateur]] before joining the [[Dunfermline Athletic F.C.|Dunfermline Athletic]] youth team at under-10 level.<ref name = "profile">{{cite web|url=http://www.dafc.co.uk/story.php?t=Ross_Drummond&ID=8242 |title=Ross Drummond |accessdate=11 December 2015 |publisher=dafc.co.uk}}</ref> He joined the Dunfermline first-team in November 2011, making his senior debut in October 2012.<ref name = "profile"/> He moved on loan to [[Berwick Rangers F.C.|Berwick Rangers]] in February 2014.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://spfl.co.uk/news/article/berwick-bring-in-drummond/|title=Berwick bring in Drummond|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=1 November 2014|publisher=SPFL}}</ref> He re-joined Berwick for a second loan spell in October 2014.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.berwickrangersfc.co.uk/news-articles-10-oct/mn-v-east-fife-311014.html|title=Ross Back with the Borderers|date=31 October 2014|accessdate=1 November 2014|publisher=Berwick Rangers F.C.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101205228/http://www.berwickrangersfc.co.uk/news-articles-10-oct/mn-v-east-fife-311014.html|archivedate=1 November 2014|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dafc.co.uk/story.php?t=On_Loan_Ranger&ID=8070|title=On Loan Ranger|date=31 October 2014|accessdate=1 November 2014|publisher=Dunfermline Athletic F.C.}}</ref> Drummond's move to Berwick was made permanent in January 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dafc.co.uk/story.php?t=Drum_leaves_for_Rangers&ID=8220 |title=Drum leaves for Rangers |date=9 January 2015 |accessdate= 31 January 2015 |publisher=DAFC.co.uk}}</ref>

Drummond left Berwick at the end of the [[2015–16 in Scottish football|2015–16 season]],<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.berwick-advertiser.co.uk/sport/football/berwick-rangers/sheerin-and-mckinlay-pen-deals-to-sign-on-for-rangers-1-4147242 |title=Sheerin and McKinlay pen deals to sign on for Rangers |work=Berwick Advertiser |publisher=Johnston Publishing Ltd |date=6 June 2016 |accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref> signing for [[Scottish Junior Football Association|Scottish Junior]] side [[Dundonald Bluebell F.C.|Dundonald Bluebell]] shortly after.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dafc.co.uk/fixture.php?SID=U20s&D=2016-07-16&ID=963 |title=U20s vs Dundonald Bluebell |publisher=Dunfermline Athletic FC |date=16 July 2016 |accessdate=17 July 2016}}</ref>

